description:

Rarity: EPIC

Properties

Sweetishrooms is a collection of sweet and cute chibi mushrooms. They were originally mushrooms, but after several long generations, managed to grow and assimilate into humans with each of their own personalities. The cap also grows from their head naturally and it is also detachable.
